                    <div id="accordion1_collapseThree3" class="collapse" is="dmx-bs4-collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion1_headingThree" data-parent="#accordion2">
                      <div class="container">
                        <p>To recap last chapter and what makes this different, number representation is about how a number is written or expressed in a particular number system, while numeric conversion is about changing a number from one number system to another.</p>
